    <div><p><a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,714 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> will host Bandai Namco Summer Showcase 2025 on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250702T1900" target="_blank">July 2 at 12:00 p.m. PT / 3:00 p.m. ET</a>, the company <a href="https://twitter.com/BandaiNamcoUS/status/1939323159766782430" target="_blank">announced</a>. You will be able to watch it on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fSoTEO-ntF8" target="_blank">YouTube</a>. <span id="more-976823"></span></p><p>The broadcast will feature a brand-new <em>My Hero Academia</em> game reveal, an exclusive trailer for <em><a title="Games > Towa and the Guardians of the Sacred Tree [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/towa-and-the-guardians-of-the-sacred-tree">Towa and the Guardians of the Sacred Tree</a></em>, a gameplay deep dive into <em><a title="Games > Digimon Story: Time Stranger [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/digimon-story-time-stranger">Digimon Story: Time Stranger</a></em>, and many other titles including <em><a title="Games > Code Vein II [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/code-vein-ii">Code Vein II</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > The Blood of Dawnwalker [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-blood-of-dawnwalker">The Blood of Dawnwalker</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Death Note: Killer Within [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/death-note-killer-within">Death Note: Killer Within</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Everybody's Golf: Hot Shots [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/everybodys-golf-hot-shots">Everybodyâ€™s Golf: Hot Shots</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Little Nightmares III [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/little-nightmares-iii">Little Nightmares III</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > PATAPON 1+2 REPLAY [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/patapon-1-2-replay">PATAPON 1+2 REPLAY</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Shadow Labyrinth [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/shadow-labyrinth">Shadow Labyrinth</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > Super Robot Wars Y [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-robot-wars-y">Super Robot Wars Y</a></em>, and <em><a title="Games > Tekken 8 [57 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tekken-8">Tekken 8</a></em> (<a href="https://twitter.com/TEKKEN/status/1939325514033811866" target="_blank">Navigating Fahkumram</a>).</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>Bandai Namco Summer Showcase 2025</span></h2><p><iframe title="Bandai Namco Summer Showcase Coming July 2!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zNFuG1BpViI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
